## Ferguson's Location API for exchanging location data with internal Ecommerce platforms and 3rd party companies.

&nbsp;&nbsp;
> ### Fetch summary list of locations via pagination:
```js
[GET]/v2/locations  
[GET]/v2/locations?page=1
[GET]/v2/locations?page=2&size=100 (max size of 100)
```
